originalText.text: Will not stay there again. I went there on a New York trip using an Air BNB. The lady was barely contacting us. The apartment was falling apart. The door handles kept coming off, the bed was broken and there was not enough room for 5 people. We could barely get in and out of the apartment safely. I would not choose this place again. It wasn't my choice to begin with. Everything was crammed into a small apartment so it seemed like it could fit everyone comfortably. It was a joke and not worth the money
